        <name>lexicographicalOrder</name>
        <qualifiedname>MR.UniformSamplingSettings.lexicographicalOrder</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>if true process the points in lexicographical order, which gives tighter and more uniform samples; if false process the points according to their ids, which is faster </para>
        </detaileddescription>
